freetext.HEALTHCARE_VISITS_OTHER: 6mo old baby received a virtual visit for rash that began 1-2 days following my vaccine.
freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: My 6mo old baby who is exclusively breastfed got a red raised rash surrounding her mouth and on her neck beginning 1-2 days following my Covid vaccine. Unsure if it is related but sharing knowing that this vaccine has not been well studied in lactating women.
No symptoms today, but did not receive a survey the day after my vaccine at which time I had chills, muscle aches, fatigue, nausea.
